com.ziluck.factions.data

Class LoadFactionStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ziluck.factions.data.LoadFactionStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FactionStore
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MongoFactionStore

    public abstract class LoadFactionStore
extends Object
implements FactionStore
    The in-memory representation of a FactionStore.

    To help reduce clutter and duplicate code, FactionStores have an additional middle step between the interface and the implementation that loads information to the database.

    Author:
    Michael Ziluck
